name: JS Paginator
body:
### JS Paginator.
The easiest way to create beautiful pagination for your site.

####Clone the project
```
$ cd your_repo_root
$ git clone https://github.com/Bentino/js_paginator.git
```

####Update the project
```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Authors and Contributors
